{"word":"G4468 - ῥᾳδιουργία - rhaidiourgía - hrad-ee-oorg-ee'-a - Mischief","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ῥᾳδιουργία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>rhaidiourgía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hrad-ee-oorg-ee'-a"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Mischief"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பொல்லாங்கு - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. ease in doing, facility"},{"paragraph":"2. levity or easiness in thinking and acting; love of a lazy and effeminate life"},{"paragraph":"3. unscrupulousness, cunning, mischief, villany"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the same as <a href=\"#/G4467 - ῥᾳδιούργημα - rhaidioúrgēma - hrad-ee-oorg'-ay-mah/4467\">G4467</a>; <i>recklessness</i>, that is, (by extension) <i>malignity:</i> - mischief."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4467 - ῥᾳδιούργημα - rhaidioúrgēma - hrad-ee-oorg'-ay-mah/4467\">G4467</a>, <a href=\"#/G4468 - ῥᾳδιουργία - rhaidiourgía - hrad-ee-oorg-ee'-a/4468\">G4468</a>"}]}